### ===========================
### RECIPES - Pruebas de endpoints
### ===========================
### Reemplazar {{TOKEN}} con el token real del login/register

### 1. Crear receta completa (con ingredientes, pasos y grupos)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/recipes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Pasta Carbonara",
  "description": "Receta italiana clásica",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/carbonara.jpg",
  "prepTime": "30 minutos",
  "servings": 4,
  "ingredients": [
    { "name": "Pasta", "quantity": "400g" },
    { "name": "Huevos", "quantity": "4 unidades" },
    { "name": "Queso parmesano", "quantity": "100g" }
  ],
  "steps": [
    { "description": "Hervir agua con sal" },
    { "description": "Cocinar la pasta al dente" },
    { "description": "Batir huevos con queso" },
    { "description": "Mezclar pasta con huevos fuera del fuego" }
  ],
  "groupIds": []
}

### 2. Obtener todas las recetas (ordenadas alfabéticamente)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/recipes

### 3. Obtener solo mis recetas (requiere token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/recipes?mine=true
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### 4. Buscar recetas por título
GET http://localhost:3000/api/recipes?search=pasta

### 5. Obtener receta por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/recipes/1

### 6. Actualizar receta
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/recipes/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Pasta Carbonara Clásica",
  "servings": 6,
  "ingredients": [
    { "name": "Pasta rigatoni", "quantity": "500g" },
    { "name": "Huevos", "quantity": "6 unidades" },
    { "name": "Queso pecorino", "quantity": "150g" },
    { "name": "Guanciale", "quantity": "200g" }
  ],
  "steps": [
    { "description": "Hervir agua con sal abundante" },
    { "description": "Cocinar la pasta al dente" },
    { "description": "Dorar guanciale en sartén" },
    { "description": "Batir huevos con queso" },
    { "description": "Mezclar todo fuera del fuego" }
  ]
}

### 7. Agregar receta a grupos
POST http://localhost:3000/api/recipes/1/groups
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "groupIds": [1]
}

### 8. Quitar receta de un grupo
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/recipes/1/groups/1
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### 9. Eliminar receta
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/recipes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
